race.comment: MISS SARA JANE (3) has a strong record this trip with 13 wins and five placings from 24 starts. In the money last time at this track (19.85) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a nose second. Appeals as a leading chance in this. JUNIPER ROSE (6) goes very well here including six wins. Was out of placings last time (31.45) at Q Parklands in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 23 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. DAINTREE GODDESS (8) beaten last start over the 390m at this track but finished in the minors in a decent 21.86. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. AUBURN QUEEN (2) generally performs well here at this distance.
